{"tid":1771964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網民號召下周一「三罷」及10區開花「黎明行動」","createTime":"2019-12-06T08:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T17:32:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3c23740b3d17a8882ef6534e2c417a6c1597fe29","tid":1771964,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/修例風波-網民號召下周-三罷-及10區開花-黎明行動-144500870.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8-%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E5%8F%8A10%E5%8D%80%E9%96%8B%E8%8A%B1-%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-144500870.html&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=e05e2341\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/修例風波-網民號召下周-三罷-及10區開花-黎明行動-144500870.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Dmy8znBF_t4HgerUWqKgOw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191205a224535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDmy8znBF_t4HgerUWqKgOw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191205a224535.jpg&h=f46138ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上月反修例、反警察示威者發起「三罷」和連串「黎明行動」期間，全港衝突此起彼落，交通命脈包括吐露港公路及紅隧癱瘓，市民仍然記憶猶新。有網民就號召，要求政府周日晚上限期前回應訴求，否則下周一即12月9日，發動新一輪「三罷」和升級版「黎明行動」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民號召，下周一清晨6時開始，示威者10區開花，早大埔、沙田、屯門、荃灣、觀塘、深水埗、黃大仙、將軍澳、油尖旺、灣仔發起「三罷」。<br />\n<br />\n亦有網民號召，早上7時至10時「塞鐵加塞路」，去到中午12時再「和你lunch 」升級版，「返工嘅手足做盾，勇武做劍，全面set roadblock、裝修、裝飾、目標係提早放工。收咗工嘅手足可以做掩護，勇武手足走先，目標達成就可走」。"},{"pid":"285f90c536ce3a207cd5dcb19d1f21fa852b3d7a","tid":1771964,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T08:41:54.000Z","msg":"星島都報<br />\n咁啲狗應該會自己塞住條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d413ec04e27823d923